    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i see what u mean about the pros and cons. but like, given how fast the climate is actually changing, is it even a real debate anymore? like, can we actually afford to wait for renewables to scale up enough to replace everything, or is nuclear basically just a necessity at this point?",
